CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, St. Louis edition, August 16, 1947, pg. 17, reads: "Still More Night of Stars - ...Right: The champ, Joe Louis, with daughter Jackie, wife Marva, and Leonard Reed, with whom Joe scored a big hit on the stage at Syria Mosque in Pittsburgh during the 'Night of Stars.' - Teenie Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Dr. Reginald Dixon, Bill Nunn Sr., unknown man in background, boxer Joe Louis with hands on shoulders of his daughter Jackie Louis, Marva Louis, and Leonard Reed, posed in hallway of Syria Mosque for "Night of Stars" production
